{"word":"G3663 - ὁμοιοπαθής - homoiopathḗs - hom-oy-op-ath-ace' - Of like passions","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὁμοιοπαθής</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">homoiopathḗs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hom-oy-op-ath-ace'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Of like passions</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"போலப் பாடுள்ள - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"அப்படியே, அந்தப்படியே, போல - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"suffering the like with another"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3664 - ὅμοιος - hómoios - hom'-oy-os/3664\">G3664</a> and the alternate of <a href=\"#/G3958 - πάσχω - páschō - pas'-kho/3958\">G3958</a>; <i>similarly affected:</i> - of (subject to) like passions.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2552/2552\">G2552</a>, <a href=\"#/G2553/2553\">G2553</a>, <a href=\"#/G3356/3356\">G3356</a>, <a href=\"#/G3663/3663\">G3663</a>, <a href=\"#/G3804/3804\">G3804</a>, <a href=\"#/G3805/3805\">G3805</a>, <a href=\"#/G3806/3806\">G3806</a>, <a href=\"#/G3958/3958\">G3958</a>, <a href=\"#/G4236/4236\">G4236</a>, <a href=\"#/G4310/4310\">G4310</a>, <a href=\"#/G4777/4777\">G4777</a>, <a href=\"#/G4834/4834\">G4834</a>, <a href=\"#/G4835/4835\">G4835</a>, <a href=\"#/G4841/4841\">G4841</a>"}]}